# Privacy Policy – Convertool

**Last updated:** February 14, 2026

---

## 1. Introduction

This Privacy Policy describes how the **Convertool** application ("App") handles user information. By using the App, you agree to the terms described in this policy.

Convertool respects your privacy and is committed to providing a simple, secure, and transparent experience.

---

## 2. Data Collection and Storage

* **Local Processing:** Unit conversions are performed **locally on your device**.
* **No personal data required:** Convertool **does not require account creation** and **does not request personal information**.
* **No proprietary servers:** The App **does not send, store, or process your data on external servers** maintained by the developers.
* **No automatic personal data collection:** Convertool **does not collect personal information**, and **does not use cookies, trackers, or third-party analytics** to monitor usage.

**Advertisements (if applicable):**
The App may display ads through third-party advertising networks. These networks may collect technical information such as device identifiers (for example, Advertising ID) and usage data to provide and personalize ads. Please refer to the respective advertising network privacy policies for more details.

Ads, if present, may be removable through a premium version or subscription.

---

## 3. Use of Data

Convertool processes information **only for the internal functionality of the App**, including:

* Performing unit conversions (length, weight, volume, temperature, etc.);
* Updating related units in real time;
* Saving user preferences locally (such as language or interface settings, when applicable).

The developers **do not use your data for advertising, marketing, profiling, or external analytics purposes**.

---

## 4. Data Sharing

* **No personal data is shared** with third parties for commercial or marketing purposes.
* Any sharing of conversion results must be performed **manually by the user**, using the operating system’s sharing features (if available).
* Advertising networks may receive technical information according to their own policies when ads are displayed.

---

## 5. User Control

You have full control over the App data:

* Preferences and settings can be modified or reset within the App;
* Any locally stored data is removed when the App data is cleared or when the App is uninstalled;
* No user account or external data retention exists.

---

## 6. Security

Since Convertool operates locally, no personal data is transmitted to external servers.

To enhance security, we recommend:

* Keeping your device protected with a password, pattern, or biometric authentication;
* Keeping your operating system updated;
* Avoiding the use of modified or untrusted versions of the App.

---

## 7. Children’s Privacy

Convertool is intended for general audiences. The App **does not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13 years of age**.

---

## 8. User Rights

At any time, you may:

* Stop using the App;
* Clear App data from your device;
* Uninstall the App, which removes all locally stored information.

For any privacy-related questions or requests, you may contact us.

---

## 9. Changes to This Policy

This Privacy Policy may be updated due to improvements in the App or changes in legal requirements. The most recent version will always be available within the App and/or on the official app store listing.

---

## 10. Contact

For questions, suggestions, or privacy-related inquiries:

**Email:** [samirtf.dev@gmail.com](mailto:samirtf.dev@gmail.com)

---

